   alla skrymsel och vrån är täckta med damm
   och det spelar ingen roll hur mycket vi dammsuger

DESCRIPTION
    self-hosted map of stockholm with manually annotated
    places which I think are neat.

    find out for yourself at https://skrymsel.missbr.uk
    (if you know swedish that is --- otherwise have fun?)

SERVER SETUP
    first make sure docker is installed.

    we download all the maps first:

    ./scripts/download_maps

    then crop to stockholm bbox and convert to tiles:

    ./scripts/maps_to_tiles

    then start the tilemap-gl server, either using run.sh
    or by setting up the docker compose.

WEBSITE SETUP
    create pins in markdown (examples in the /pins folder).

    install python requirements:

    pip3 install -r requirements.txt

    run build script:

    python3 build.py

    by default it creates the static website under /serve.
    otherwise you can specify it:

    python3 build.py /path/to/serve/dir

CRED
    theme's basically a stripped down version of
    https://github.com/openmaptiles/osm-bright-gl-style

    config/lua ripped straight from tilemap
    https://github.com/systemed/tilemaker

